dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Menominee County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase NMenominee_Roads_2018.gdbN. [Road segments representing centerlines of all roadways or carriageways in a local government. Typically, this information is compiled from orthoimagery or other aerial photography sources. This representation of the road centerlines support address geocoding and mapping. It also serves as a source for public works and other agencies that are responsible for the active management of the road network.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
